"this app is a measly 24kb of WASM (uncompressed), compared to 274kb in non-"
"islands mode. (274kb is quite large for a “Hello, world!” It’s really just "
"all the code related to client-side routing, which isn’t being used in the "
"demo.)"
msgstr ""

